{"tid":484579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收錢拒作供　單親媽判囚","createTime":"2017-11-30T08:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T10:05:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a238f5467e44c01626192817637953ec1a1e515","tid":484579,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230079&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2x4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=1b5a4ea4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230079&h=90390ef0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230079</a><br />\n<br />\n收錢拒作供　單親媽判囚<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171130/large/18087348.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F18087348.jpg&h=56978367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單親媽媽收錢同意不出庭頂證持刀鄰居，遭官斥浪費警力和無視法紀。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】27歲單親媽媽2014年遭鄰居持刀恐嚇，事後她扮失憶拒出庭指證鄰居，對方最終脫罪。警方發現單親媽媽收了數千元同意不出庭頂證。持刀鄰居、單親媽媽及中間人早前承認妨礙司法公正罪，法官昨斥被告浪費警力和嚴重影響法庭威信，無視法紀，判囚13個月2周至21個月。<br />\n被告為持刀鄰居鄭偉民（37歲）、單親媽媽陳嘉欣、中間人陳國雄（43歲）及陳寶如（55歲）。法官指鄭是始作俑者，兼犯藏毒罪，共判刑21個月；另斥陳嘉欣只向錢看，指示家人收錢犯罪，判監14個月。另兩人負責傳遞訊息及交收金錢，判囚13個月零2周及14個月。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC456/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲、歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"68be8c38478553056c9d4324fcc4d40951cc7c43","tid":484579,"uid":24044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"27e6c0b733e8770921afa615148d49cc655bb4d4","tid":484579,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"一定係中學被人中出既無腦mk妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 要幾on9要覺得收個幾千 唔出庭作證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}